query:
SELECT places.place_id, places.house_number
                FROM places
                WHERE NOT EXISTS (
                    SELECT 1
                    FROM tickets
                    WHERE tickets.place_id = places.place_id
                    AND (
                        (tickets.start_date <= $2 AND tickets.end_date >= $1)
                        OR (tickets.start_date <= $1 AND tickets.end_date >= $2)
                        OR (tickets.start_date >= $1 AND tickets.end_date <= $2)
                    )
                )
